### Question 2: What will be printed when you run the following code?

```java
class Test{
   public static int i=10;
   public static void main(String[] args){
       System.out.print(i++ + ++i);
   }
}
```

#### Answer:

The value of `i` will be incremented twice before printing to console. So the answer would be **12**

### Question 3: What will be printed when you run the following code?

```java
class Test{
   public static int i=10;
   public static void main(String[] args){
      System.out.print(--i + --i);
   }
}
```

#### Answer:

The value of `i` will be decremented twice before printing to console. So the answer would be **8**

